      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "#p406# says that I’ve grown a lot since my last visit. She’s starting to give me slightly tougher tasks than before. First, she mentions that #p410#, the owner of the potion shop, has run out of ingredients while working on a new potion. He needs me to hunt #b40 #o18#s#k and #b40 #o19#s#k, and collect #b20 #t4000018#s#k and #b20 #t4000019#s#k. Taking on #o18# might be a bit tricky, but it shouldn’t be too much trouble for me!"
