  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "You're the one that helped me take care of #b#p414##k's request, right? He should be enjoying his seafood soup right about now... But hey, you look much stronger than before! Alright, if that's the case... you can probably take care on some tougher gigs now."
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirName": "1",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "I have a new job for you, actually. #b#p410##k of Famous Pharmacy needs help. He's been working on creating a new potion, and one day, he realized he's out of ingredients. Those are pretty hard to find, and he claims that it's slowing down his experiments..."
      },
      "2": {
        "_dirName": "2",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "He wants to get the ingredients quickly so he can continue his research. He needs you to hunt #r40 #o18#s#k and #r40 #o19#s#k, and collect #b20 #t4000018#s#k and #b20 #t4000019#s#k... That shouldn’t be too difficult for someone like you. Come see me once you’ve gathered everything. I’ll be waiting!"
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "I knew it... I knew you could get it done quickly! You did your job well last time, and here you are again, taking care of business! Alright, since you have done so well, I should reward you well. #b#p410##k is giving you #b30 #t2000002#s#k to help you in the future."
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Alright, if you need work sometime down the road, feel free to come back and see me."
        }
      },
      "stop": {
        "_dirName": "stop",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
